IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User developmentpetar@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass smtp.gmail.com"
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.emacs.d/Mail/
Inbox ~/.emacs.d/Mail/Inbox

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns "INBOX" "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Drafts" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/All Mail" "[Gmail]/Trash"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
